## Workflow

Work entirely by reading files and writing `memory.md` / `idea.md`. Do not
execute code. Use the curiosity anchor as the region to explore, but choose a
meaningfully different mechanism rather than a parameter tweak. For nearby
runs, inspect `discovered/loss.py`, `notes.md`, and `run.log`, with attention
to both raw metrics and each normalized value.

